 *
 * 🎯 PROPÓSITO:
 * Diagrama de secuencia que muestra el flujo completo
 * de un pedido desde que el cliente escanea el QR
 * hasta que el restaurante recibe la notificación
 * por WhatsApp.
 *
 * 📦 NOTA:
 * Este archivo debe ser renderizado con PlantUML
 *
 * 🔗 RELACIONES:
 * - Visualiza el flujo de negocio principal
 *
 * 📋 HISTORIAL DE CAMBIOS:
 * ------------------------------------------------------
 * 1.0 - 2024-01-17 02:30
 *    ✅ Creación inicial del diagrama
 *    ✅ Flujo de pedido a domicilio
 *    ✅ Flujo de pedido desde mesa
 *    ✅ Manejo de caché y colas
 * ======================================================
 */

@startuml MENU_QR_PLUS_SEQUENCE
!theme plain

title MENU QR PLUS - Diagrama de Secuencia (Pedido a Domicilio)

' ======================================================
' ACTORES Y PARTICIPANTES
' ======================================================

actor "Cliente" as Client #FFE8E8
participant "Frontend\n(React)" as Frontend #F0F0F0
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway #F0F0F0
participant "Menu Service" as MenuService #F0F0F0
database "Redis\n(Caché)" as Redis #E8FDE8
database "PostgreSQL\n(Read Replica)" as DBRead #E8FDE8
database "RabbitMQ\n(Cola)" as Queue #E8FDE8
participant "Order Service" as OrderService #F0F0F0
participant "WhatsApp Service" as WhatsAppService #F0F0F0
actor "Dueño" as Owner #FFE8E8

' ======================================================
' FLUJO: OBTENCIÓN DEL MENÚ
' ======================================================

== 1. Acceso al menú ==

Client -> Frontend: Escanea QR / Abre link
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Gateway: GET /:slug/menu
activate Gateway

Gateway -> MenuService: Obtener menú
activate MenuService

MenuService -> Redis: Buscar menú en caché
activate Redis

alt Caché encontrado
    Redis --> MenuService: Retorna menú cacheado
else Caché no encontrado
    Redis --> MenuService: null
    MenuService -> DBRead: SELECT * FROM categories + products
    activate DBRead
    DBRead --> MenuService: Retorna categorías y productos
    deactivate DBRead
    MenuService -> Redis: Guardar en caché (TTL 5min)
    MenuService --> Redis
end
deactivate Redis

MenuService --> Gateway: Retorna menú formateado
deactivate MenuService

Gateway --> Frontend: 200 OK + menú
deactivate Gateway

Frontend --> Client: Muestra menú interactivo

' ======================================================
' FLUJO: ARMADO DEL PEDIDO
' ======================================================

== 2. Cliente arma el pedido ==

Client -> Frontend: Agrega productos al carrito
Frontend -> Frontend: Actualiza estado local (Zustand)

Client -> Frontend: Procede al checkout

' ======================================================
' FLUJO: ENVÍO DEL PEDIDO
' ======================================================

== 3. Envío del pedido ==

Client -> Frontend: Completa datos y confirma
Frontend -> Gateway: POST /order
activate Gateway

Gateway -> OrderService: Crear pedido
activate OrderService

OrderService -> DBRead: Validar productos y precios
activate DBRead
DBRead --> OrderService: Productos validados
deactivate DBRead

OrderService -> OrderService: Calcular totales

alt Tipo domicilio
    OrderService -> OrderService: Verificar cobertura
end

OrderService -> DBRead: INSERT INTO orders (pending)
activate DBRead
DBRead --> OrderService: Pedido creado
deactivate DBRead

OrderService -> Queue: Publicar mensaje en cola
activate Queue
Queue --> OrderService: Mensaje encolado
deactivate Queue

OrderService --> Gateway: 201 Created
deactivate OrderService

Gateway --> Frontend: { order_id, order_number }
deactivate Gateway

Frontend --> Client: Pedido recibido, abriendo WhatsApp...

' ======================================================
' FLUJO: PROCESAMIENTO ASÍNCRONO
' ======================================================

== 4. Procesamiento en segundo plano ==

Queue -> OrderService: Consumir mensaje
activate OrderService

OrderService -> DBRead: Obtener datos completos
activate DBRead
DBRead --> OrderService: Datos del pedido
deactivate DBRead

OrderService -> WhatsAppService: Generar mensaje
activate WhatsAppService

WhatsAppService -> WhatsAppService: Formatear pedido

WhatsAppService --> OrderService: Mensaje listo
deactivate WhatsAppService

OrderService -> DBRead: UPDATE orders SET status = 'confirmed'
activate DBRead
deactivate DBRead

OrderService -> WhatsApp: Abrir enlace wa.me
OrderService --> Queue: Confirmar procesamiento

deactivate OrderService

' ======================================================
' FLUJO: NOTIFICACIÓN AL RESTAURANTE
' ======================================================

== 5. Restaurante recibe el pedido ==

WhatsApp -> Owner: Mensaje con detalle del pedido
Owner -> Owner: Confirma y prepara pedido

' ======================================================
' NOTAS ADICIONALES
' ======================================================

note over Client, Owner
  <b>Tiempos estimados:</b>
  - Carga del menú: < 500ms (con caché)
  - Creación del pedido: < 300ms
  - Procesamiento async: < 2s
  - Notificación WhatsApp: inmediata
end note

@enduml